 src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：已批出不反對反對政府通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ddae8ee7bf2c1ad57e14aa3a5f2ef63b89f684","tid":2081315,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"90年代(97前)取消左,之後臨時立法會恢復"},{"pid":"fb38b8d9d6c37484ceb7e15a2b4cd81dfa2d5726","tid":2081315,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92ddae8ee7bf2c1ad57e14aa3a5f2ef63b89f684","tid":2081315,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"90年代(97前)取消左,之後臨時立法會恢復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"臨時立法會仲恢復左公安條例,取消新9組,集體談判權,租務管制"},{"pid":"60dfddaa48507beed64cbcd1c1b4b7202db0e796","tid":2081315,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79dac76d7e7b644d50279f10fda52c720cb78f85","tid":2081315,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"咁若果講明集會係49人，分100 批唔同地點舉行有無得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"㗎下係冇理可講時代"}]}